  <data name="Home_About_P2" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>According to analysts at US magazine Global Finance, WebMoney was named the best bank of 2024.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Home_About_P3Intro" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>WebMoney also received multiple awards at the “Bank of the Year” ceremony for 2023, announced in 2024:</value>
